    <TD><B><FONT face="Book Antiqua"><FONT color=#000066><FONT 
      size=+3>Goal</FONT></FONT></FONT></B>　&nbsp; 
      <UL>
        <LI>A General Purpose Multi-User Main Memory Object Storage System </LI></UL>　　&nbsp; 
      <P><B><FONT face="Book Antiqua"><FONT color=#000066><FONT size=+3>Features 
      and Characteristics</FONT></FONT></FONT></B>　&nbsp; 
      <UL>
        <LI>All the Objects reside in Main Memory 
        <LI>Supporting Variable Length Objects
        <LI>T-tree Indexing
        <LI>Concurrent Access for Multiple Users 
        <LI>Robust WAL-Based Crash Recovery with Record (Object) Level Locking 
	<LI>Multi-threaded Architecture
        </LI></UL>
                <p align="center">&nbsp;<IMG height="384" 
      src="hermes.files/hermes_st_eng.gif" width="512"> 
      <P><B><FONT face="Book Antiqua"><FONT color=#000066><FONT 
