      <UL>
        <LI>Real-Time Database Management Systems 
        <LI>Home Location Registration(HLR) 
        <LI>Mobile Computing 
        <LI>Factory Automation(FA)
        <LI>CIM <BR>　　　 　　　　　　&nbsp; 
      <BR>　</LI></UL>
      <P><B><FONT face="Book Antiqua"><FONT color=#000066><FONT size=+3>Expected 
      Results</FONT></FONT></FONT></B>&nbsp; 
      <UL>
        <LI>Core technological know-how for Real-Time Database Management System </LI></UL>&nbsp; 
